170114,62,720,2,18,1,130,15,"Atha rājā tamatthaṃ sutvā mānathaddho eso mama vijite nisīdāpetuṃ vaṭṭati, raṭṭhantaraṃ pabbājetabboti rājāṇāya raṭṭhantaraṃ pesesi. "
170115,62,721,2,8,1,47,6,Rājapurisā ca taṃ pakkosetvā raṭṭhantaraṃ ānesi. 
170116,62,721,9,31,1,167,19,"Bahaṅgaṃ nāma desaṃ patvā bahaṅganāyako puriso rājapurisānaṃ lañjaṃ datvā evamāha,- ayaṃ pana bhonto marammaraṭṭhassa pariyantappadeso, idheva ṭhapetvā tumhe nivattathāti. "
