170125,62,725,20,54,1,242,29,"Sace tvaṃ mahārāja maṃ māretukāmo pakkoseyyāsi, evaṃ sati yadi sikkhaṃ appaccakkhāya ṭhitaṃ maṃ māreyyāsi, tava bhāriyaṃ kammaṃ bhavissatīti manasikaritvā tava kammassa abhāriyatthāya sikkhaṃ paccakkhitvā āgatomhi, sace maṃ māretukāmosi, mārehīhi. "
