170193,62,755,13,32,1,169,18,"Yasmā pana sabbesaṃ therānaṃ nāmaṃ uddharitvā visuṃ visuṃ kathite ayaṃ sāsanavaṃsappadīpikakathā atippapañcā bhavissati, tasmā idha ajjhupekkhitvā vattabbameva vakkhāmāti. "
