170231,62,769,22,43,1,148,18,"Athassa etadahosi,- idāni mama pātheyyaṃ khayaṃ ahosi, imasmiṃ kira raṭṭhe sahassorodhagāme laddhavaro nāma mahāseṭṭhi sabbattha bhūtale ativiya pākaṭo. "
170232,62,769,44,66,1,166,20,"Tassāhaṃ ñātīti vañcetvā kathessāmi, evaṃ sati tena mahāseṭṭhinā mittasanthavaṃ kātuṃ tetegāmikā manussā mama bahu lābhaṃ dassanti, tadā pātheyyena akiccho bhavissāmīti. "
170233,62,769,67,80,1,134,13,Evaṃ pana cintetvā antarāmagge sampattasampattagāmesu mahābhogānaṃ gehaṃ vicinetvā mahābhogānaṃ santikaṃ pavisitvā kathāsallāpaṃ akāsi. 
170234,62,770,2,18,1,81,13,"Atha tetegāmikā tvaṃ kuto āgato, kuhiṃ gamissasi, kassa ñāti, ko vā tvanti pucchiṃsu. "
