170241,62,771,39,44,1,41,5,Laddhavaro mahāseṭṭhi tena na diṭṭhapubbo. 
170242,62,771,45,72,1,245,26,Sahassorodhagāmaṃ sampatteyeva ayaṃ kiṃ nāma gāmoti apucchitvāyeva tasmiṃ gāme mahābhogatarassa mahāgehaṃ vicinanto tasseva laddhavarassa seṭṭhino mahantaṃ gehaṃ passitvā laddhavarassa seṭṭhino santikaṃ pavisitvā tena saddhiṃ kathāsallāpaṃ akāsi. 
