170252,62,777,61,79,1,165,18,Evaṃ pana pucchanto so mayā pubbe vuttaṃ tīsu vinayamahāṭīkāsu sādhakavasena dassitaṃ cūḷagaṇṭhipadaṃyeva idanti vacanaṃ saccamevāti mukhāsuññatthāya punappunaṃ vadi. 
