170255,62,779,17,28,1,102,11,Atha parasenāya yujjhitvā parasenā abhibhavitvā sabbe manussā attano attano abhimukhaṭṭhānaṃ palāyiṃsu. 
170256,62,779,29,38,1,69,9,Atha sopi puriso tena sahāyena saddhiṃ attano abhimukhaṭṭhānaṃ palāyi. 
