170613,62,944,32,41,1,86,9,Visesato pana vassantarajātakakathaṃ te manussā bahūhi dātabbavatthūhi pūjetvā suṇanti. 
170614,62,945,2,15,1,121,12,"Tañca mahāraṭṭhaṃ nāma syāmaraṭṭhasamīpe ṭhitaṃ, teneva syāmaraṭṭhavāsinopi bhikkhū gahaṭṭhāca yebhuyyena sotuṃ icchantīti. "
170615,62,945,16,31,1,194,13,"Mahādhammarakkhitattheropi mahāraṭṭhavāsīhi saddhiṃ sakalasyāmaraṭṭhavāsīnaṃ dhammaṃ desesi, amatarasaṃ pāyesi, yathā yonakadhammarakkhitatthero aparantaraṭṭhaṃ gantvā sakalamarammaraṭṭhavāsīnanti. "
170616,62,946,2,16,1,120,12,"Yaṃ pana yonakaraṭṭhasāsanavaṃsakathāyaṃ vuttaṃ, tampi sabbaṃ etthāpi daṭṭhabbaṃyeva, tehi tassa ekasadisattena ṭhitattāti. "
170617,62,946,17,25,1,85,8,Tathā hi nāgasenattheropi yonakaraṭṭhe vasitvā syāmaraṭṭhādīsupi sāsanaṃ patiṭṭhāpesi. 
